        "class": "",
        "text": "). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "The great God",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The epithet belongs to the writer rather than to Ezra himself, who in his own book never uses it. It recurs in this section (",
        "children": []
