        "text": "1 Chronicles 16:8",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". To this thanksgiving the people answered Amen, Amen (comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 16:36",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), lifting up their hands (ידיהם בּמעל, with lifting up of their hands; the form מעל occurring only here), and worshipping the Lord, bowing down towards the ground.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  }
